###########MECHANICAL MODELS AVAILABLE
###########
########### Notched 3PB
########### !! pro 3PB zadej mindist ve fracture zone (zbytek bude hrubsi) !!
########### A: 1131/200, B: 1386/300, C: 800/100
###########Model 2d_notched3pb Xsize 0.8 Ysize 0.2 notchH 0 loadWidth 0.005 minDist 0.01 fracZoneWidth 0.08 activeMechanics 1 orthogonalFracZone 0 trials 10000 notchWidth -1
###########Model 3d_notched3pb Xsize 1.386 Ysize 0.3 Zsize 0.1 notchH 0 loadWidth 0.05 minDist 0.03 fracZoneWidth 0.5 activeMechanics 1  orthogonalFracZone 0 trials 200 notchWidth -1
###########
###########
###########3d cube
###########Model 3d_cube Xsize 1.0 Ysize 1.0 Zsize 1 minDist 0.1 powerTes 1 activeMechanics 1 activeTransport 1 coupled 1 trials 10000
###########
###########RWTH Notched 3pb
###########
########### A: 0.5/0.2/0.1, B: 1.0/0.4/0.1  ///  0.525   1.050
###########Model 2d_notched3pb Xsize 0.525 Ysize 0.2 notchH 0.16667 loadWidth 0.005 minDist 0.008 fracZoneWidth 0.08 activeMechanics 1 orthogonalFracZone 0 trials 100000 notchWidth 0.008
###########Model 3d_notched3pb Xsize 1 Ysize 0.4 Zsize 0.1 notchH 0.16667 loadWidth 0.01 minDist 0.008 fracZoneWidth 0.05 activeMechanics 1 orthogonalFracZone 0 trials 10000 notchWidth 0.008 elasticZone 1 
###########
###########
########### Dogbones ########### pro normalni model roughDogBone 0 elasticZone 0
###########roughDogBone >1 : kolik je hodnota, tolikanasobek minDist jemneho modelu bude na kazdou stranu od prostredku modelu nahoru a dolu
###########roughMinDistCoef 15 udava nasobek minDist, ktery je pouzit jako hrube zrno ve zhrubenych oblastech
###########interLayerThickness 100  udava vysku dodatecne oblasti v nasobku mindist nad a pod zjemnenym prostredkem, kde je plynuly prechod mezi jemnou zrnitosti a hrubou zrnitosti
########### roughEdgeDogbone 0 - presne nasamplovane kruznice
########### roughEdgeDogbone 1 - prvky s obema nody v modelu
########### roughEdgeDogbone 2 - prvky s obema nody v modelu, ozrcadlene
###########Model 2d_dogbone dogboneD 0.5 minDist 0.004 dogboneExcentricityFrac 50 activeMechanics 1 trials 1200 symmetric 0 edgeMinDistCoef 0.9 roughDogBone 15 elasticZone 1 roughEdgeDogbone 1 randomizeMaterial 1 roughMinDistCoef 5 interLayerThickness 20 nr_models 50 defaultFilesFolder dogboneDefault
###########0.125
###########Model 2d_dogbone dogboneD 0.8 minDist 0.006 dogboneExcentricityFrac 50 activeMechanics 1 trials 1000 symmetric 0 edgeMinDistCoef 0.9 roughDogBone 1 elasticZone 1 roughEdgeDogbone 0 randomizeMaterial 1 roughMinDistCoef 5 interLayerThickness 1 nr_models 100 defaultFilesFolder dogboneDefault
###########C
###########Model 2d_dogbone dogboneD 0.8 minDist 0.006 dogboneExcentricityFrac 50 activeMechanics 1 trials 3000 symmetric 1 edgeMinDistCoef 0.7 roughDogBone 10 elasticZone 1 roughEdgeDogbone 0 randomizeMaterial 1 roughMinDistCoef 8 interLayerThickness 60 nr_models 200 defaultFilesFolder dogboneDefault
###########
###########DOGBONE STRIP
########### roughDogBone 0 - ekvidist grid, catch corners
########### roughDogBone 1 - random, catch corners
########### roughDogBone 2 - random 
###########Model 2d_dogboneStrip dogboneD 0.4 minDist 0.006 dogboneExcentricityFrac 50 activeMechanics 1 nr_models 400 roughDogBone 1 defaultFilesFolder dogboneDefaultStrip
###########
###########DOGBONE BAND
###########Model 2d_dogboneBand minDist 0.001 Xsize 60 Ysize 10 activeMechanics 1  roughMinDistCoef 2 elasticHeightCoef 2 nr_models 100 defaultFilesFolder dogboneDefaultBand
###########
###########Model 3d_dogbone dogboneD 0.1 minDist 0.010 dogboneExcentricityFrac 50 activeMechanics 1 
###########Model 3d_dogbone dogboneD 0.1 minDist 0.010 dogboneExcentricityFrac 50 activeMechanics 1
###########
########### Cusatis torsion press
Model 3d_cylinderTorsionPress cylinderHeight 0.4445 cylinderRad 0.1183 minDist 0.025 activeMechanics 1 activeTransport 1 coupled 1 trials 10000 powerTes 1
###########
###########
########### Noguiera torsion
###########Model 3d_cylinderTorsionPress cylinderHeight 0.150 cylinderRad 0.0375 minDist 0.003 activeMechanics 1 trials 50000 elasticZone 0.25
